Title: Evil from the Seas
Description: I do not know what this evil is that is infesting the forest, $n, but I know exactly how to deal with it. So do you, I think.
ObjectivesText: Kill 8 Darkened Horrors or Darkened Terrors.
RewardText: You make me proud, $n. You make all of us proud.

Objectives.Text: Darkened Horrors or Darkened Terrors slain
